TableDefinition.DatabaseQuery: SELECT u_a_d.UserApplicationDataID, u.UserName, a.ApplicationName, u_a_d.UserApplicationDataName AS 'Account Profile', MAX(CONVERT(DATETIME,SWITCHOFFSET(CONVERT(DATETIMEOFFSET,l.LogTime),DATENAME(TZOFFSET,SYSDATETIMEOFFSET())))) AS 'Last started' FROM UserApplicationData u_a_d INNER JOIN Users u ON u_a_d.UserID = u.UserID INNER JOIN Applications a ON a.ApplicationID = u_a_d.ApplicationID INNER JOIN UserApplicationDataVariables u_a_d_v ON u_a_d_v.UserApplicationDataID = u_a_d.UserApplicationDataID AND u_a_d_v.VariableName = a.VariableToDisplay LEFT JOIN LogApplication l_a ON l_a.ApplicationID = a.ApplicationID LEFT JOIN Log l ON l.LogApplicationID = l_a.LogApplicationID WHERE u.UserId = '1' GROUP BY u_a_d.UserApplicationDataID, u.UserName, a.ApplicationName, u_a_d.UserApplicationDataName
